text = "Left Mouse Button:   Click and drag tiles
Space:   Speak your sentence early


🌊🌊    From the deep you come to speak on behalf of all crabdom.    🌊🌊

Now is your chance to convince the chefs of the world to put down their crackers and boiling pots and to join claw with hand in peace.

As Crabvocate, speak to the humans by dragging tiles into the bottom row.

Your translator is on the left, prompting you with persuasive human grammar.

Can you keep your composure or will you simmer under the heat?"
horizontal_alignment = 1

